('GI Bill Education Benefits', 'gi-bill-education', 'Use your GI Bill benefits to pursue education and training, including college degrees, vocational training, and certifications.', 'Education', 'benefit', 'https://www.va.gov/education/about-gi-bill-benefits/', 'Department of Veterans Affairs', 'Veterans with at least 90 days of active duty service after 9/10/2001', 'yes'),

Job fairs, career workshops, and networking opportunities nationwide.', 'Career', 'organization', 'https://www.hiringourheroes.org/', 'U.S. Chamber of Commerce Foundation', 'Veterans, transitioning service members, and military spouses', 'yes'),

('Mental Health Resources', 'mental-health-resources', 'Confidential mental health support including counseling, crisis intervention, and peer support for veterans.', 'Healthcare', 'benefit', 'https://www.mentalhealth.va.gov/', 'VA Mental Health', 'All veterans', 'yes')
